Locations on the other server are shown in red, locations on this server are green.

You can assign one of your slots to be your home waypoint on the Amia: Abroad (AmiaB) server. You will enter this area when using the door in the entry. 

The default home waypoint is either slot 2 (if you are member of a faction) or slot 1. Your custom home point will be marked with two stars (**). Make sure your bindoint is on the Amia: Abroad server!
